        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1384558933,
        "creation_date": 1384558933,
        "body": "<p>In netbeans use this question <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2875983/how-do-i-configure-netbeans-to-only-step-through-java-code-that-ive-written?rq=1#answer-2876131\">How do I configure NetBeans to only step through Java code that I&#39;ve written<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>In eclipse go to <\/p>\n\n<p>Window->Preferences->Java->Debug->Step Filtering    <\/p>\n\n<p>Check the box to \"Use Step Filters\" and check all the boxes for packages you dont want to go into.<\/p>\n",
        "answer_id": 20012595,
        "question_id": 20012564,
